The paper proposes a new method for semantic instance segmentation using deep learning techniques. The paper focuses on developing a similarity metric based on a deep, fully convolutional embedding model and a grouping method based on selecting all points that are sufficiently similar to a set of "seed points" chosen from a deep, fully convolutional scoring model. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is computer vision (cs.CV), followed by machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and multimedia (cs.MM).
